				"number": 2,
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"37016\"></a>Evidensbaserad farmakologisk behandling av olika ångestsyndrom enligt en systematisk litteraturöversikt gjord av SBU<a class=\"tableFootnoteLink\" href=\"#fnote_28\"><sup>a</sup></a> (2)",
				"id": "s2_38",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Ångestsyndrom</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>SSRI</strong></div></td><td><p><strong><div class=\"tableLine\">Övriga <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">antidepressiva</div></strong></p></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Buspiron</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Hydroxizin</strong></div></td><td><p><strong><div class=\"tableLine\">Benso-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">diazepiner</div></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Paniksyndrom</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Specifika fobier</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Social fobi</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">3</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Tvångssyndrom</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Posttraumatiskt </div><div class=\"tableLine\">stressyndrom</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Generaliserad ångest</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">3</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">2</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"6\" class=\"footNotes\"><div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_28\">a. För förklaring av evidensstyrka enligt graderingen 1–3 se Tabell 1 <a href=\"#25606\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-mini pageLink\"><i class=\"fa fa-arrow-right fa-white\"></i></a>.</div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
